name: Self Similarity
description: Created by @mathmakesart (https://mathmakes.art) on 2020-07-26. This piece is a 1920 by 1080 grid of pixels whose colors have been individually manipulated through a sixteen-times-repeated application of a specific RGB filter function. After this many applications of the function, a series of self-similar geometries begin to emerge. From this piece I have created 10 different variants which will subsequently be minted as single-edition NFTs and listed for sale at a price of 1.0 XTZ each.
